ff]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I guess they’ll let ANYBODY in here</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/wJBTzF1</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GfyndZq.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/wJBTzF1</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ElbowDeepInACentaur]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Crazy comes in all shapes, sizes, and genders!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/xPh3mH1</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/vIWMB8S.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Watching the Heard/Depp trial has been an unhappy trip down memory lane. 

Way back in 2007/2008 I used to Dungeon Master a D&D campaign for a bunch of people I went to the goth bars with. It was a mixed group of men and women. I ended up dating one of the girls but it ended up ending pretty badly after just a few months. We had been drinking, and had a fairly minor disagreement one night. I left to go chill out in my bedroom to de-escalate. I was in my late 20s, didn't have a lot of money, so my bed was a mattress and a boxer on the floor. She followed in after me, kicked me in the back, called me a "pussy" and said she had my wallet. She was threatening to throw it out the window of my apartment 23 floors up. I was pretty shocked and upset I'd just been assaulted, plus I didn't live in a great neighborhood so the thought of my wallet flying out into the night was upsetting. I got up, insisted she give it back, and when I got too close she pulled a battle axe off the wall and started threatening me with it (remember I said I was a D&D nerd right? My apartment was decorated with medieval weapons).  

I'm a big guy but I legit felt threatened, so I leaped forward and grabbed the axe, because shit - she'd already kicked me - what else was she capable of? I'd rather not end the evening getting hit with an axe. We struggled, and in the course of struggling the haft of the axe hit her in the face. She ended up with a black eye that lasted for a week and a half.  

I didn't mean to hurt her, but I was angry and scared, and no way was I going to let somebody pull my own axe on me in my own apartment! So in the end I disarmed her, she dropped the wallet, and then she called some middle aged sugar daddy I hadn't known about previously to come get her. He ended up coming into my apartment to give me hell too. 

Long story long I ended up loosing all of those friends, and others, because "I gave my girlfriend a black eye". Not one of those people ever bothered reaching out to get my side of the story. I have no doubt she played the entitled victim and ran my name through the mud. I learned about fair weather friends that day. 

And I also learned that crazy comes in all sizes, shapes, and genders. So when I hear Johnny's testimony about Amber chasing after him, room after room, escalating and forcing conflict I believe him.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/xPh3mH1</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[bluegoatrampant]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Du-dump</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/5kVHMXX</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Brl0GOc.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dYGSnt5.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Whoops, sorry. Not a goat!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3axYqsU.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/u8Yrhmb.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MeMr3LA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/mfaHUyz.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/hp758pF.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KL9Vkty.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/WfaXIYA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/aJFB1F6.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HjipgLq.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bIq3GSK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UiH99Dj.jpg" style="ma